00:52:11,410 --> 00:52:22,550
♫  I'll keep you in my arms and say I'll protect you forever  ♫

574
00:52:28,460 --> 00:52:33,170
I'll be back... safely.

575
00:53:16,010 --> 00:53:20,020
&lt;ㅑ&gt;

576
00:53:25,420 --> 00:53:29,860
 Maiden Hong Joo, may I enter for a moment?

577
00:53:30,980 --> 00:53:33,810
Yes, come in.

578
00:53:48,520 --> 00:53:52,100
They said the jesters would be visiting the market today.

579
00:53:52,100 --> 00:53:54,290
I am looking forward to it already.

580
00:53:54,290 --> 00:53:56,820
Well, Maiden Hong Joo...

581
00:53:56,820 --> 00:53:59,770
What's wrong?

582
00:53:59,770 --> 00:54:03,700
An important matter suddenly came up.

583
00:54:03,700 --> 00:54:06,890
Let us go watch the jesters next time.

584
00:54:06,890 --> 00:54:12,190
There's no choice if it's an important matter.

585
00:54:12,190 --> 00:54:14,850
Take care.

586
00:54:14,850 --> 00:54:17,440
It is a huge relief, though.

587
00:54:23,800 --> 00:54:30,620
If I missed this beautiful sight of you, I would have been quite disappointed.

588
00:55:02,830 --> 00:55:06,690
I am worried you might get hurt.

589
00:55:16,770 --> 00:55:18,720
Lower your swords.

590
00:55:26,360 --> 00:55:30,720
Chief Administrator Jang seeks to make an urgent report to His Majesty.

591
00:55:35,330 --> 00:55:37,900
You can hand it to me.

592
00:55:37,900 --> 00:55:40,750
It is a report regarding Lee Seol.

593
00:55:40,750 --> 00:55:44,040
I intend to hand it directly to His Majesty.

594
00:55:54,490 --> 00:55:58,390
I did not write it down, worried it might get leaked.

595
00:55:58,390 --> 00:56:01,160
Leaked to whom?

596
00:56:01,160 --> 00:56:03,890
Left State Minister Shin Won Ho...

597
00:56:03,890 --> 00:56:07,240
That man is the sponsor of Mok In Hoe.

598
00:56:11,080 --> 00:56:16,980
Shin Won Ho is... attempting to put Lee Seol on the throne.

599
00:56:17,800 --> 00:56:22,260
Head Eunuch and... Queen Dowager joined his cause, too.

600
00:56:22,260 --> 00:56:26,740
So we do not know how many more spies exist within the palace.

601
00:56:36,200 --> 00:56:38,960
Will you be able to prove what you said?

602
00:56:38,960 --> 00:56:42,130
I have a witness in custody.

603
00:56:42,130 --> 00:56:45,640
You can question him when you return to the palace.

604
00:56:48,940 --> 00:56:56,500
Your Majesty... should I not also be informed if it is an urgent report on Lee Seol?

605
00:56:56,500 --> 00:56:58,410
Left State Minister...

606
00:56:59,340 --> 00:57:03,830
You said you would give your life up to me. Right?

607
00:57:03,830 --> 00:57:08,690
I said I would do so if I failed to catch Lee Seol within this month.

608
00:57:18,020 --> 00:57:20,590
That is enough for me.

609
00:57:20,590 --> 00:57:23,210
I must go back to the palace now.

610
00:57:39,550 --> 00:57:45,320
 They are trying to kill me and put Lee Seol on the throne?

611
00:57:46,920 --> 00:57:49,430
Your Majesty!

612
00:57:49,430 --> 00:57:52,450
- Escort His Majesty! 
 -  Yes!

613
00:58:01,740 --> 00:58:03,230
Let us go.

614
00:58:03,230 --> 00:58:05,960
I'll escort you to the gates.

615
00:59:07,050 --> 00:59:10,540
You finally came, Lee Seol.

616
00:59:25,010 --> 00:59:31,890

617
00:59:49,150 --> 00:59:51,210

618
00:59:51,210 --> 00:59:54,530
 It was all my fault from the beginning to the end.

619
00:59:54,530 --> 00:59:58,580
 Did you kill my son and play around with his betrothed?

620
00:59:58,580 --> 01:00:01,680
 Please do not forgive me. Blame me and hate me, please.

621
01:00:01,680 --> 01:00:05,860
 If you intend to stay as Ihwawon's hostess, you two will part ways.

622
01:00:05,860 --> 01:00:08,800
 Could you live the rest of your life without San?

623
01:00:08,800 --> 01:00:13,200
 Lee Seol, I will not have to stand here again if you bring down the king.

624
01:00:13,200 --> 01:00:16,290
 I promise you. I'll come back before the sun sets.

625
01:00:16,290 --> 01:00:21,100
 I will not be taken down and come to you safely.

